
### Find all People
GET localhost:9090/api/person


### Find all Person with ID 1 (PathVariable)
GET localhost:9090/api/person/1

### Find all People FAIL - 404 Status Code
GET localhost:9090/asdasdas

### Create a Person
POST localhost:9090/api/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Simon",
  "email": "simon@lexicon.se"
}

### Delete Person by ID
DELETE localhost:9090/api/person/34


### Update Person (PathVariable + RequestBody)
PUT localhost:9090/api/person/1

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Simon",
  "email": "simon@lexicon.se"
}

### Update Person (PathVariable & RequestParam)
PATCH localhost:9090/api/person/1?name=Simon Elbrink

### find with email(RequestParam)
GET http://localhost:9090/api/person/email?email=simon@LEXICON.se




